Class Statistic

  • java.lang.Object
    • nc.com.analyzer.Statistic

  • public class Statistic
extends java.lang.Object
    A Statistic contains information about type of sort, type of array and list of each of times that means sorting array of 10, 100, 1000 or 10000 elements.
